recipe.label: Chicken and Pineapple Salad
ingredientLines: 12 ounces shredded and poached or store-bought roasted chicken (about 3 cups)
1 small head napa cabbage (1 1/2 pounds), halved lengthwise and finely shredded crosswise
1/2 small pineapple prepared, and thinly sliced crosswise

recipe.label: ASIAN CHICKEN SALAD WITH GRILLED PINEAPPLE
ingredientLines: 1 tablespoon soy vay teriyaki sauce (or your preference)
2 brown kumato tomatoes- or any flavorful tomato quartered
1 fresh pineapple cut in to disks (best to use a corer)
